properties.text: TITLE OF THE GAME - THE GREATEST TITLE EVER!

instanceVariables.Name: Tutorials are poop.
instanceVariables.Description: Don't expect me to hold your hand in this game.

instanceVariables.Name: Asteroid Field
instanceVariables.Description: This is your first real test, Pilot! You have to navitgate through this treacherous asteroid field, but I'm sure with your incredible weaponry, you'll do just fine! It's only the first level of the game after all... how hard could it really be?

instanceVariables.Name: Level 2
instanceVariables.Description: No fun game has just one level. You made it through the tutoria;l... you braved the daunting trials of level 1. Now go ahead, brave soul... make your way onward... to LEVEL TWO!!!

instanceVariables.Name: The... THIRD level! (of the game)
instanceVariables.Description: Descriptionis are quite descriptive when you're trying to describe things, but when you're not... they're kinda useless. Good luck with the third level! :'D

instanceVariables.Name: Fight Night
instanceVariables.Description: Everything is in space... it's always night! Also there are enemies that will try to kill you. If you haven't learned how to shoot by now, then you better figure it out.

instanceVariables.Name: Purple People Eaters
instanceVariables.Description: The title has nothing to do with what's going to be in this level. Sadly, there are no purple people eaters in the game. There are more enemies in this level though... the enemies are probably not going away any time soon, so you'd better get used to them.

instanceVariables.Name: Spikes, Spikes, and EVEN MORE SPIKES!!!
instanceVariables.Description: For once, there is an apt title and description for a level. You will encounter lots of pointy things here. I do not reccomend touching them.

instanceVariables.Name: Video Game Physics
instanceVariables.Description: Did you take that class yet?

instanceVariables.Name: Die. I want you dead.
instanceVariables.Description: We are not friends anymore. I'm going to kill you over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over and over.........

instanceVariables.Name: The enemies are gone.
instanceVariables.Description: Forever! I promise... I won't try to kill you anymore if you didn't like the last level. I'll only be exceedingly nice to you from here on out. As a gesture of goodwill, this level is just a puzzle!
